text: Semitrochatella is a genus of land snails with an operculum, terrestrial gastropod mollusks in the family Helicinidae. == Species == Species within the genus Semitrochatella include: * Semitrochatella alboviridis (Wright in Pfeiffer, 1864)"Mollusca" . Diversidad Biológica Cubana, accessed 23 March 2011. * Semitrochatella babei (Arango, 1876) * Semitrochatella conica (Pfeiffer, 1839) * Semitrochatella elongata (d’Orbigny, 1842) * Semitrochatella fuscula (Gundlach in Pfeiffer, 1863) == References == Category:Helicinidae
title: Semitrochatella
